seo: 深信服EDR,任意管理员登录漏洞,漏洞检测,网络安全
seo_en: Sangfor EDR, arbitrary admin login vulnerability, vulnerability detection, network security
summary: 该插件用于检测深信服EDR系统中的任意管理员登录漏洞，通过发送特定请求判断是否存在漏洞并返回相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the arbitrary admin login vulnerability in Sangfor EDR system. It sends specific requests to determine if the vulnerability exists and returns related information.
